                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6307" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0978</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8348 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康恩贝转让珍视明部分股权：鱼与熊掌能否兼得？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Conba transfers part of Zhenshiming&#39;s equity: Can you have your cake and eat it?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱春艳，张郁昕，付苗，许楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江康恩贝制药股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康恩贝；珍视明；长期股权投资；成本法；权益法</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Conba;zhenshiming; Long - term equity investment; Cost method; Equity method</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当今世界正处于不断变化的时代，随着全球格局的变迁和疫情的扩散，有企业因难以适应这种变化而最终倒闭，也有企业为了维持经营而选择售卖子公司。在2021年的年底，康恩贝就将持有珍视明42%的股权转让，最终对珍视明的持股由80%降为38%。令人奇怪的是，作为老牌药企康恩贝手下的得力干将，珍视明为其业绩立下汗马功劳，如今却被转让，究竟是母公司康恩贝将其扫地出门，还是子公司珍视明想要另寻高就？康恩贝转让珍视明与其他为了盈余管理、资金获取而剥离子公司的行为动机上是否有差异？本案例以康恩贝转让珍视明的部分股权为主线，在综合分析康恩贝经营现状以及内外部环境基础上，系统剖析其转让背景、转让条件，以及最终的结果，试图探究康恩贝转让珍视明部分股权的深层次原因。本文旨在通过对案例前因后果的梳理，使学生理解并掌握长期股权投资的核算方法、以及不同的核算方法之间转换的会计处理和对财务报表的影响，同时引导学生从财务维度和战略维度探讨康恩贝转让珍视明股权的影响，最终加深学生对企业风险的认识与思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Nowadays, the world is in an ever-changing era. With the change of the global pattern and the spread of the epidemic, some enterprises have finally closed down because it is difficult to adapt to this change, and some enterprises have chosen to sell their subsidiaries in order to maintain their operations. At the end of 2021, Conba will transfer 42% of the shares of Zhenshiming, and finally the shares of Zhenshiming will be reduced from 80% to 38%. Strangely, as the right-hand man under the old pharmaceutical company Conba, Zhenshiming made great contributions to its performance, but now it has been transferred. Is it the parent company Conba who drives it out, or is it the subsidiary Zhenshiming who wants to find another job? Is there any difference between Compay&#39;s motivation of transferring Zhenshiming and other behaviors of divesting subsidiaries for earnings management and capital acquisition? This case takes Conba&#39;s transfer of part of Zhenshiming&#39;s equity as the main line. On the basis of comprehensive analysis of Conba&#39;s operating status and internal and external environment, it systematically analyzes its transfer background, transfer conditions and the final result, trying to explore the deep-seated reasons for Conba&#39;s transfer of part of Zhenshiming&#39;s equity. The purpose of this paper is to make students understand and master the accounting methods of long-term equity investment, as well as the accounting treatment of the conversion between different accounting methods and its impact on financial statements by sorting out the causes and effects of the case. At the same time, it will guide students to explore the impact of Conba&#39;s transfer of Zhenshiming&#39;s equity from the financial dimension and strategic dimension, and finally deepen students&#39; understanding and thinking about enterprise risks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《中级财务会计》、《高级财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长期股权投资的核算由成本法转权益法；两种核算方法的区别；长期股权投资成本法转权益法的会计处理；核算方法改变对财务报表的影响；母公司转让子公司的风险；如何规避这种风险；母公司转让子公司的原因以及影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
